{"word":"G629 - ἀπολύτρωσις - apolýtrōsis - ap-ol-oo'-tro-sis - Deliverance","slug":"G629","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπολύτρωσις</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>apolýtrōsis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ap-ol-oo'-tro-sis"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Deliverance"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03BB;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C4;&#x03C1;&#x03C9;&#x03C3;&#x03B9;&#x03C2; - apolutro&#x0304;sis</b> - <i>ap-ol-oo'-tro-sis</i><p/>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G3083\">G3083</a>; (the act) <i>ransom</i> in full, that is, (figuratively) <i>riddance</i>, or (specifically) Christian <i>salvation:</i> - deliverance, redemption."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G179\">G179</a>, <a href=\"#/G1955\">G1955</a>, <a href=\"#/G1956\">G1956</a>, <a href=\"#/G2646\">G2646</a>, <a href=\"#/G2647\">G2647</a>, <a href=\"#/G3083\">G3083</a>, <a href=\"#/G3084\">G3084</a>, <a href=\"#/G3085\">G3085</a>, <a href=\"#/G3086\">G3086</a>, <a href=\"#/G3089\">G3089</a>, <a href=\"#/G359\">G359</a>, <a href=\"#/G360\">G360</a>, <a href=\"#/G487\">G487</a>, <a href=\"#/G630\">G630</a>"}]}